title: Arbor Skateboards :: Product Profiles - Vugenhausen
description:
The Vügenhausen is a top mount built for speed. It offers superior traction and leverage over your trucks for race level performance. A stiff, symmetrical platform and gas pedals give you superior turn and drift control, with a micro drop and rocker for locked-in performance.
Artist: Eric Waetzig

L: 37.00” W: 9.75” WB: 28.00-29.00”
To learn more about the Vugenhausen visit: arborcollective.com/skateboards/products/vugenhausen/
